<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1905-04-26T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1905-04-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="336" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d336">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Dawson</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Santo
                                        Domingo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-04-26"><hi rend="italic">April 26,
                                1905</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p rend="flushleft"><hi rend="smallcaps">Secretary of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington:</hi></p>
                        <p>Colton arrived. Presented. Conference with Dominican authorities was
                            satisfactory.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Dawson.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>